, Stanford <br />\n再做 post doc<br />\n而且發表過多人 quote 既 paper 係高 impact journal<br />\n仲有識得點出到大量 publications 同申請 funding <br />\n有 network 請到優質研究生<br />\n識得點 manage research project 同研究生<br />\n咁應該可以有機會爭到教席<br />\n<br />\n你依家 phy 讀到咩程度？</blockquote><br />\n宇宙既形成"},{"pid":"18a77122be76d630d5d214a4635002dde4723852","tid":174340,"uid":86347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T03:31:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>資料科學家你制唔制？<br />\n定係你想做自然科學嗰類</blockquote><br />\n我想讀phy做物理學家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁首先要名大學 first hon<br />\n香港的話最少三大 first hon<br />\n然後美國名大學 PhD, 如Harvard, Stanford <br />\n再做 post doc<br />\n而且發表過多人 quote 既 paper 係高 impact journal<br />\n仲有識得點出到大量 publications 同申請 funding <br />\n有 network 請到優質研究生<br />\n識得點 manage research project 同研究生<br />\n咁應該可以有機會爭到教席<br />\n<br />\n你依家 phy 讀到咩程度？</blockquote><br />\n痴線邊洗first hon <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d711dc210726ecddaa1075cd58a0e339be670c52","tid":174340,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T03:33:04.000Z","msg":"請睇隔離 research post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/171284/page/15?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/171284/page/15?ref=android</a>"}]}